To add a time signature change to Reaper:

#Place the song position pointer where you would like the change to take place.
#Go to '''Insert/ Time signature [or] tempo change marker'''

[[File:Reaper tempo and time signature menu.png]]


In the box that appears you can customize the change, including its placement if you would like it somewhere else other than where the song position pointer is placed. 




